# Trade Lifecycle Glossary

| Term | Definition | Example |
|------|------------|----------|
| Trade | Financial agreement between two parties. | FX Forward |
| Trade Capture | Recording trade into Murex. | Trader books trade |
| Trade Validation | Checking business rules before processing. | Credit Limit Validation |
| Static Data | Master data used by the system. | Currency |
| Market Data | Dynamic market information. | USD/INR Rate |
| Pricing | Calculation of trade value. | FX Pricing |
| Position | Net quantity held. | Long USD |
| Hedging | Offset trade to reduce exposure. | Sell USD |
| Exposure | Current financial risk. | USD 58M |

