| Term | Definition |
|------|------------|
| Incident | Unexpected production issue. |
| RCA | Root Cause Analysis. |
| Batch | Scheduled background process. |
| Job Failure | Scheduled process failed. |
| Alert | Warning generated by monitoring system. |
| Monitoring | Continuous health check of applications. |
| Escalation | Forwarding issue to higher support level. |
| Validation | Verification of system correctness. |
| Investigation | Finding root cause of an issue. |

